{
 "name": "RPlog_Morganna_in_the_Hospital",
 "title": "Morganna in the Hospital",
 "summary": "At Dr. Tarquin Memorial Hospital, the Imperial Joir arrives flanked by bodyguards to visit the critically wounded Ambassador Morganna, who lies sedated with a bandaged, reconstructed throat after being shot. Conferring with the attending medic, Joir learns that she is stable but very weak, with throat-reconstruction surgery planned for the following day. Though his face stays impassive, Joir's concern for the Ambassador's life shows in his voice as he studies her medical charts, the medic marveling that she survived such grievous wounds at all. The visit reveals the cold Imperial's quiet investment in Morganna's survival.",
